{"tid":1309523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"⬤ 已故影星尤敏與丈夫合葬龕位遭破壞，骨灰被盜","createTime":"2019-07-12T08:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T15:57:20.000Z","uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1df755d1db390b53a2e450d6538e218170f92853","tid":1309523,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:44:37.000Z","msg":"跑馬地黃泥涌道香港墳場，今日(12日)下午1時許，有市民到拜祭先人時，發現已故女星尤敏與丈夫高福球合葬的骨灰龕位遭到破壞，雲石面被扑爛，懷疑骨灰及陪葬品被盜去，於是報警。警方接報到場，同時發現另一個骨灰龕位亦遭破壞，警員在附近一帶兜截，惜無發現，案件暫列盜竊案處理，目前正點算損失財物價值，並追緝涉案人士歸案。<br />\n<br />\n尤敏生於1936年，1996年去逝，原名畢玉儀，粵劇名伶白玉堂是其父親，任劍輝則是其表姑。其丈夫高福球，其父親是港澳著名實業家、慈善家，廣東省番禺沙溪官涌人，於港澳地區開設多家典當鋪，有省港澳「典當業大王」之稱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e6/%E5%B0%A4%E6%95%8F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe6%2F%25E5%25B0%25A4%25E6%2595%258F.jpg&h=3c236508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.picclickimg.com/d/l400/pict/352655521797_/50s-%E7%84%A1%E8%AA%9E%E5%95%8F%E8%92%BC%E5%A4%A9-%E5%B0%A4%E6%95%8F-Hong-Kong-Chinese-movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.picclickimg.com%2Fd%2Fl400%2Fpict%2F352655521797_%2F50s-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AA%259E%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%2592%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E5%25B0%25A4%25E6%2595%258F-Hong-Kong-Chinese-movie.jpg&h=334b67b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星星月亮太陽(1961)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/lobo801091/1378655509-2554919279_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Flobo801091%2F1378655509-2554919279_n.jpg&h=4364b237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港之夜(1961)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/photo/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190712162544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190712162544&h=e435f755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩個骨灰龕位被扑毀兼盜竊。(張世洋攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/photo/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190712162544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190712162544&h=bc2b5e7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n骨灰龕位面寫有畢玉儀及高福球的名字。(張世洋攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/photo/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190712162544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190712162544&h=3d0e3b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中一個遭破壞兼盜竊的骨灰龕位。(張世洋攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/photo/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190712162544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190712162544&h=0c160c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一個骨灰龕位亦遭毀爛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/photo/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_05p.jpg?20190712162544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20190712162544&h=8d33690a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員到場調查。（張世洋攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/photo/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_06p.jpg?20190712162544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20190712162544&h=d52dc022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港墳場現盜墓賊。（張世洋攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/photo/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_07p.jpg?20190712162544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_07p.jpg%3F20190712162544&h=5408a505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n墳場有2個骨灰龕位損毀。(張世洋攝)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fbkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001.html&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyiKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=c1a5fd50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4c85a3c963b81d13e9cbdd8fd5f7e61f03323487","tid":1309523,"uid":52972,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/photo/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_05p.jpg?20190712162544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20190712162544&h=8d33690a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆個骨灰龕要2個白衫4個藍衫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n差佬真易做"},{"pid":"b2a0521fe388fd80e08e6227bf4cf1d425acdf63","tid":1309523,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c85a3c963b81d13e9cbdd8fd5f7e61f03323487","tid":1309523,"uid":52972,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/photo/bkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_05p.jpg?20190712162544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190712142552266-0712_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20190712162544&h=8d33690a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆個骨灰龕要2個白衫4個藍衫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n差佬真易做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07